<P>
   GETAWAY _ Is the new Beau Rivage Resort and Casino in Biloxi,
Miss., all its cracked up to be? Is it as beautiful as Elizabeth
Taylor suggests in those moonlight and magnolia TV ads? We visit to
find out. (It is beautiful, but a lot of gliches need to be ironed
