   MUSIC-MCBRIDE (Undated) _ As anyone who's heard Martina
McBride's hits _ such as ``Independence Day'' and ``A Broken Wing''
_ can attest, she can hold her own with the most powerful female
country singers in Nashville, from Patty Loveless and Wynonna Judd
to Trisha Yearwood and Faith Hill. Her new album is due in
Septmeber. By RICK MITCHELL.
</P>
<P>
   TV-MTV-REAL-WORLD (Undated) _ A new season of ``The Real World
premieres'' Tuesday night on MTV, and if the first episode is any
indicator, expect this cast to bring back the ``reality'' that made
the show's early seasons so captivating. By PAMELA MITCHELL.
</P>
