meets with Major League Baseball's Executive Committee. Steve Rock.
.MDNM/ WILL. On the eve of the Chiefs' weekend minicamp, defensive
lineman Dan Williams talks about the frustration of last year's
holdout and admits there were no winners in the final tally. Randy
Covitz. 22-25.
