r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CLINTON-KOSOVO-0611-C     06-10 0533
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CLINTON-KOSOVO-0611-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: This story will be updated after President Clinton's speech
at 8 p.m. EDT.
 &HT;    CLINTON: FINISH THE JOB, BUILD THE PEACE IN KOSOVO, BALKANS
