cycles; price, $22 per class or $80 for four, including post- and
pre-class parties. There are also private lessons, $65 to $79 an
hour, or less for special packages. Tango salon, with dancing to
recorded music, every Sunday night from 8 to 11 at the studio;
cover, $10. There are also tango parties at the studio every
Wednesday night, with dancing from 9:30 to midnight; cover, $10.
</P>
<P>
   DANCE MANHATTAN, 39 W. 19th St., fifth floor, Chelsea, (212)
