   FILM-BESIEGED &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Maybe Bernardo Bertolucci's days of plumbing new
depths in the medium are behind him. Yet there's a radiance, a
sureness of touch coupled with his astonishing taste and style,
that makes ``Besieged'' a unique pleasure. It glows. By ELVIS
MITCHELL. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
