   FILM-HARMLESS SEX &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Picking on a film like this feels kind of like
bullying, but the truth is that ``Just a Little Harmles Sex'' is
just a little needless movie. The acting is OK at best, the
direction static despite some nifty camera movements, courtesy of
veteran cinematographer Bruce Surtees. By ROBERT PHILPOT. Story has
moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
