   FILM-POWERS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ The ``Austin Powers'' movies have become this
generation's ``Pink Panther'' films. And let's not forget, the
endless repetition of those films turned into an industry. By ELVIS
MITCHELL. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
