<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990610.0252 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-10 18:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0723 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-BBO-HALLOFF     06-10 0034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
