plans to move for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs
of Friday, June 11 and thereafter. The stories will carry the ``f''
financial news category code unless otherwise noted. For questions
about stories, contact Susan Leh at the Daily News, (818) 713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   TECH-PARK (Moorpark) _ A developer plans to spend $40 million
building a high-technology industrial park in Moorpark to
capitalize on the spillover of companies from the West San Fernando
Valley and Ventura County looking for room to grow. The 33-acre
project will be adjacent to the 23 Freeway. By Gregory Wilcox.
