<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Baptists to show faith in evangelism
 &HT;    By Gayle White
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ If the doorbell rings this weekend when you're not
expecting company, chances are it's a Southern Baptist.
</P>
<P>
   About 40 Southern Baptist churches in metro Atlanta will be
coordinating door-to-door canvassing Saturday through Wednesday as
