<HEADLINE>
EDITORIAL: A LONG, HOT SUMMER SCHOOL 
</HEADLINE>
   (af)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The New York Times says in an editorial Friday, June 11: &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Each day seems to bring more dreary news about New York City's
public school system. Unfortunately, these excruciating details
about how poorly many of the city's students fare on new
